{{Lunisolar March}} '''March 2''' is the 2nd day of the month {{ill|March (Lunisolar)|ja|3月 (旧暦)|lt=March (Yayoi)|12=draft|12=draft}}, the 3rd month of the traditional {{ill|Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|12=draft|12=draft}}. Its {{ill|Rokuyō|ja|六曜|12=draft|12=draft}} day is {{ill|Butsumetsu|ja|仏滅|12=draft|12=draft}}.
== Events == * [[Empress Jitō]] 9th year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} [[695]] {{ill|April 19|ja|4月19日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}) – In this year, the king of 【新羅】 sent a prince as an envoy to Japan.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://example.com|title=Reference needed|accessdate=2021-03}}</ref> * [[Engen]] 1st year / [[Kenmu]] 3rd year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} [[1336]] {{ill|April 13|ja|4月13日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}) – In the battle of Tatara-hama, after being chased from Kyoto, [[Ashikaga Takauji]] defeated Kikuchi Takefusa at Chikuzen Tatara-hama and resumed his eastward advance. * {{ill|Tenpō|ja|天保|12=draft|12=draft}} 11th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} [[1840]] {{ill|April 4|ja|4月4日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}) – Under the appointment of {{ill|Mizuno Tadakuni|ja|水野忠邦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}, the office of the Kanjō Bugyō was transferred to the position of the Kita-machi Bugyō.
== Births == * [[Tendoku (Japan)|Tendoku]] 3rd year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} [[959]] {{ill|April 12|ja|4月12日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Emperor Enyū|ja|円融天皇|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}, the 64th Emperor of Japan (died [[991]]). * [[Ryakuō]] 1st year / [[Engen]] 3rd year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} [[1338]] {{ill|March 23|ja|3月23日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Emperor Gōgen|ja|後光厳天皇|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}, the 4th Emperor of the Northern Court (died [[1374]]). * {{ill|Kansei|ja|寛仁|12=draft|12=draft}} 3rd year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} [[1791]] {{ill|April 4|ja|4月4日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Ansekong Saensai|ja|安積艮斎|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}, a Confucian scholar (died [[1861]]).
== Deaths == * [[Chishō]] 3rd year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} [[1179]] {{ill|April 10|ja|4月10日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Shunkwan|ja|俊寛|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}, a monk (died [[1143]]). * [[Meitoku]] 3rd year / [[Genchū]] 9th year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} [[1392]] {{ill|March 25|ja|3月25日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Hosokawa Yoriyuki|ja|細川頼之|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}, a military commander and official (died [[1329]]). * {{ill|Tenshō|ja|天正|1=Tenshō (Momoyama period)|lt=Tenshō Era|12=draft|12=draft}} 10th year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} [[1582]] {{ill|March 25|ja|3月25日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Ninashi Morinobu|ja|仁科盛信|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}, a military commander (died [[1557]]?).
