== Events == * [[Empress Jitō]] 9th year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}} [[695]] {{ill|April 19|ja|4月19日|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}}) – In this year, the king of 【新羅】 sent a prince as an envoy to Japan.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://example.com|title=Reference needed|accessdate=2021-03|qq=}}</ref> * [[Engen]] 1st year / [[Kenmu]] 3rd year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}} [[1336]] {{ill|April 13|ja|4月13日|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}}) – In the battle of Tatara-hama, after being chased from Kyoto, [[Ashikaga Takauji]] defeated Kikuchi Takefusa at Chikuzen Tatara-hama and resumed his eastward advance. * {{ill|Tenpō|ja|天保|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}} 11th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}} [[1840]] {{ill|April 4|ja|4月4日|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}}) – Under the appointment of {{ill|Mizuno Tadakuni|ja|水野忠邦|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}}, the office of the Kanjō Bugyō was transferred to the position of the Kita-machi Bugyō.
