== Births == * [[Tendoku (Japan)|Tendoku]] 3rd year ([[:en:Julian calendar|Julian calendar]] [[959]] [[:en:April 12|April 12]]) – [[:en:Emperor En'yū|Emperor Enyū]], the 64th Emperor of Japan (died [[991]]). * [[Ryakuō]] 1st year / [[Engen]] 3rd year ([[:en:Julian calendar|Julian calendar]] [[:en:1338|1338]] [[:en:March 23|March 23]]) – [[:en:Emperor Go-Kōgon|Emperor Gōgen]], the 4th Emperor of the Northern Court (died [[:en:1374|1374]]). * [[:en:Kannin|Kansei]] 3rd year ([[:en:Gregorian calendar|Gregorian calendar]] [[1791]] [[:en:April 4|April 4]]) – {{ill|Ansekong Saensai|ja|安積艮斎|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ansekong Saensai|qq=}}, a Confucian scholar (died [[1861]]).
== Deaths == * [[Chishō]] 3rd year ([[:en:Julian calendar|Julian calendar]] [[:en:1179|1179]] [[:en:April 10|April 10]]) – [[:en:Shunkan|Shunkwan]], a monk (died [[:en:1143|1143]]). * [[Meitoku]] 3rd year / [[Genchū]] 9th year ([[:en:Julian calendar|Julian calendar]] [[:en:1392|1392]] [[:en:March 25|March 25]]) – [[:en:Hosokawa Yoriyuki|Hosokawa Yoriyuki]], a military commander and official (died [[:en:1329|1329]]). * [[:en:Tenshō (Momoyama period)|Tenshō Era]] 10th year ([[:en:Julian calendar|Julian calendar]] [[:en:1582|1582]] [[:en:March 25|March 25]]) – [[:en:Nishina Morinobu|Ninashi Morinobu]], a military commander (died [[:en:1557|1557]]?).
