== Events == * [[Empress Jitō]] 9th year ([[:en:Julian calendar|Julian calendar]] [[:en:695|695]] [[:en:April 19|April 19]]) – In this year, the king of [[Silla]] sent a prince as an envoy to Japan.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://example.com|title=Reference needed|accessdate=2021-03|qq=}}</ref> * [[Engen]] 1st year / [[Kenmu]] 3rd year ([[:en:Julian calendar|Julian calendar]] [[:en:1336|1336]] [[:en:April 13|April 13]]) – In the battle of Tatara-hama, after being chased from Kyoto, [[:en:Ashikaga Takauji|Ashikaga Takauji]] defeated Kikuchi Takefusa at Chikuzen Tatara-hama and resumed his eastward advance. * [[:en:Tenpō|Tenpō]] 11th year ([[:en:Gregorian calendar|Gregorian calendar]] [[:en:1840|1840]] [[:en:April 4|April 4]]) – Under the appointment of [[:en:Mizuno Tadakuni|Mizuno Tadakuni]], the office of the Kanjō Bugyō was transferred to the position of the Kita-machi Bugyō.
== Births == * [[Tendoku (Japan)|Tendoku]] 3rd year ([[:en:Julian calendar|Julian calendar]] [[:en:959|959]] [[:en:April 12|April 12]]) – [[:en:Emperor En'yū|Emperor Enyū]], the 64th Emperor of Japan (died [[:en:991|991]]). * [[Ryakuō]] 1st year / [[Engen]] 3rd year ([[:en:Julian calendar|Julian calendar]] [[:en:1338|1338]] [[:en:March 23|March 23]]) – [[:en:Emperor Go-Kōgon|Emperor Gōgen]], the 4th Emperor of the Northern Court (died [[:en:1374|1374]]). * [[:en:Kannin|Kansei]] 3rd year ([[:en:Gregorian calendar|Gregorian calendar]] [[:en:1791|1791]] [[:en:April 4|April 4]]) – {{ill|Ansekong Saensai|ja|安積艮斎|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ansekong Saensai|qq=}}, a Confucian scholar (died [[:en:1861|1861]]).
== Deaths == * [[Chishō]] 3rd year ([[:en:Julian calendar|Julian calendar]] [[:en:1179|1179]] [[:en:April 10|April 10]]) – [[:en:Shunkan|Shunkwan]], a monk (died [[:en:1143|1143]]). * [[Meitoku]] 3rd year / [[:en:Genchū|Genchū]] 9th year ([[:en:Julian calendar|Julian calendar]] [[:en:1392|1392]] [[:en:March 25|March 25]]) – [[:en:Hosokawa Yoriyuki|Hosokawa Yoriyuki]], a military commander and official (died [[:en:1329|1329]]). * [[:en:Tenshō (Momoyama period)|Tenshō Era]] 10th year ([[:en:Julian calendar|Julian calendar]] [[:en:1582|1582]] [[:en:March 25|March 25]]) – [[:en:Nishina Morinobu|Ninashi Morinobu]], a military commander (died [[:en:1557|1557]]?).
